title: Jenkins & Jonez - KD Came At the Twitter King and Missed
itunes:title: Jenkins & Jonez - KD Came At the Twitter King and Missed
description:
John and Mike give Tyler the floor to discuss his Twitter burial of Kevin Durant (1:00) before the three of them discuss the NBA’s top 75 list, who are the biggest snubs, and why the old-head players should be removed from the list (9:00).
